{"tid":2046161,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【國安法】5大學校長發聲明撐立法 科大城大浸大無聯署","createTime":"2020-06-01T08:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T11:12:55.000Z","uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"54b14150e051b3be0dc897f4bdd7e130c2093b5d","tid":2046161,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:29:48.000Z","msg":"本港5所大學的校長今日發表聲明，表示完全支持「一國兩制」，理解訂立「港區國安法」的必要性。<br />\n<br />\n聲明由嶺南大學校長鄭國漢、中文大學校長段崇智、教育大學校長張仁良、理工大學校長滕錦光、和香港大學校長張翔聯合發出。科技大學、城市大學和浸會大學的校長並無聯署。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指出，國家及香港的繁榮穩定與年青人的未來息息相關。安全穩定的社會環境、健全法制與法治、良好治安、多元包容，對香港的長遠發展至為重要。<br />\n<br />\n5大校長表明他們完全支持「一國兩制」，理解訂立國家安全法的必要性，並珍惜基本法所保障的言論、新聞、出版及集會自由等權利。 會一如既往，堅守學術自由，卓越教研，及院校自主，並維護多元文化，貢獻社會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1785262\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1785262&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8wPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=99179116\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1785262&h=fd108558\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/hk/1785262</a>"},{"pid":"c9860410507ffd4b4b2bdec825c420737c9a6ecf","tid":2046161,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200601/_2020060114134068999.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200601%2F_2020060114134068999.jpg&h=d5ade87e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10206999b892f95d49f7c618f691aac8c289bc8d","tid":2046161,"uid":33643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a96f7c0c0b7442293625cefeed42e1014c8a2d0","tid":2046161,"uid":76404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:37:36.00